Package: TreeCorTreat
Type: Package
Title: Tree-based correlation screen for phenotype-associated transcriptomic features and cell types
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2021-10-25
Author: Boyang Zhang, Hongkai Ji
Maintainer: Boyang Zhang <bzhang34@jhu.edu>
Description: TreeCorTreat is a software tool that supports multi-resolution and multi-feature type association analysis in single-cell data. We also introduce TreeCorTreat plot as a new visualization tool to summarize the association information in such data.
Depends: R (>= 3.6.1)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
